sentences.english: To protect it, we had to backfill on it again.
sentences.chinese: 为了保护遗址，又将遗址进行了回填。

sentences.english: Saponification slag-fly ash can be used in the high fill sections of highway.
sentences.chinese: 皂化渣粉煤灰可以用做桥头等高填土路段的回填材料。

sentences.english: Backfilling shall be performed in a manner that avoids abrasion or other damage to both factory and field-applied coatings.
sentences.chinese: 回填时避免破换工厂后者现场喷涂的涂层。

sentences.english: They can be backfilled with concrete or plastered on the inside to beef them up.
sentences.chinese: 它们可以回填混凝土或灰泥在里面的牛肉他们。

sentences.english: The compact density of backfill earth in water transportation pipeline construction has to meet the requirements in design stage.
sentences.chinese: 输水管道工程回填土压实度应符合设计要求。

sentences.english: It is an actual three-dimensional structure, backfilled with sediment.
sentences.chinese: 这是一个真实的三维结构，回填与沉积物。

sentences.english: Slags containing Mn is used as the roadbed backfill instead of natural clay.
sentences.chinese: 利用含锰废渣代替天然粘土作为路基回填土。

sentences.english: Strictly forbid to backfill soil without tamping layer after layer or backfilling with replenished water directly.
sentences.chinese: 严禁回填土采取不分层夯实或向槽内灌水的方法回填。

sentences.english: Strictly forbid to backfill soil without tamping layer after layer or backfilling with replenished water directly.
sentences.chinese: 严禁回填土采取不分层夯实或向槽内灌水的方法回填。

sentences.english: After placement of the earth fill, it is almost always compacted to prevent subsequent settlement.
sentences.chinese: 回填土平整后，通常需要夯实以防止出现附加沉降量。

sentences.english: Build high anti-seep vertical well dam backfill cannel and fill concrete, etc…
sentences.chinese: 建筑高抗渗竖井，大坝回填槽，填充混凝土等。
